::Terrataur::
       She shakes her head.  She goes back in her tunnel, digging right up 
under Windlord and Starstomp.  "Hurry up Quetzalcoatl.  Get inside, quickly." 
 With that said she hops out of her tunnel and runs to Quetzalcoatl.  She 
fires two missiles at whoever is firing at him.  (I forgot who it was.)
